		<span id="comment-6a00d8341ef22f53ef0115715f0691970b-content"><p>Perry, try the pickle with la lot with beef on this site: </p>

<p><a href="http://vietworldkitchen.com/blog/2007/06/beef-in-wild-be.html" rel="nofollow">http://vietworldkitchen.com/blog/2007/06/beef-in-wild-be.html</a></p>

<p>The pickle is nice with the duck and egg noodle soup that&#39;s in Into the Vietnamese Kitchen. Another great pickle that&#39;s in the book is the tangy mixed vegetable pickle with cauliflower, red pepper, and carrot. </p></span>
